323
00:19:59,519 --> 00:20:00,200
I'll take a look.

324
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:04,840
Wait.

325
00:20:06,599 --> 00:20:07,599
Shuo Xuan.

326
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:09,080
Are you

327
00:20:10,119 --> 00:20:12,080
