602
00:38:02,919 --> 00:38:03,959
Let's go together.

603
00:38:04,560 --> 00:38:06,600
You go first
and I'll be right behind you.

604
00:38:07,239 --> 00:38:07,919
Let's go.

605
00:38:23,560 --> 00:38:25,919
