00:38:31,600 --> 00:38:32,919
I'm bound to get a little frustrated.

609
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,360
If those disciples hadn't died,

610
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:39,080
Zhaoyan could follow the clue,

611
00:38:39,600 --> 00:38:41,800
