and get the antidote.

612
00:38:42,719 --> 00:38:44,439
This way, Little Yue
wouldn't have to suffer this.

613
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:49,040
Physician Bian, do you think so?

614
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:53,159
You seem to be implying something.

